400 has the effect of causing the employer to refuse to hire or employ or to
401 bar or to discharge from employment any individual or to discriminate
402 against any individual in compensation or in terms, conditions or
403 privileges of employment on the basis of, the individual's race, color,
404 religious creed, age, sex, gender identity or expression, marital status,
